cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the problem of recovering 3D structure from 2D images. It also involves robotics (cs.RO) as camera motion estimation is a crucial aspect of the problem. Machine learning (cs.LG) is also relevant as some of the techniques discussed involve learning-based approaches. Graphics (cs.GR) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with the creation of 3D models from images. Multimedia (cs.MM) is also relevant as the paper discusses various sources of data and software for SfM.
